name: General-files
tagline: General dump for files used by Cyber@UCR. This will become more granulated as we accumulate more files.
body:
### Cyber@UCR General File Repository
These files are provided for members of Cybersecurity at the University of California, Riverside (Cyber@UCR). Distribution is unlimited on all files in this repository.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
